alerts.text: The escalator between the Grand concourse and Northern concourse is temporarily out of service. If you require assistance, please ask staff or phone 9379 1777.
alerts.title: Escalator Availability - Central

alerts.text: From 20 April to 31 May, the Suburban Tunnel will be temporarily closed for Sydney Metro construction works.  Access for Platforms 16 to 23 is only via the Northern Concourse or Southern Tunnel during this period. You can view a map of the stationhere  https://transportnsw.info/document/4930/central-station-map.pdf
alerts.title: Station Update - Central

alerts.text:
Until further notice:
- Due to infrastructure damage caused by bushfires, buses continue to replace trains between Lithgow and Mount Victoria.
- Trains continue to run between Bathurst, Lithgow, and and Central, to a changed timetable.

Please use transport apps or visit transportnsw.info for details.
alerts.title: Trackwork - Blue Mountains Line
